## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ba238-158">다음 코드 예제를 다시 설정의 기하학적 변환을 `pgBrush` id입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ba238-158">The following code example resets the geometric transform of `pgBrush` to identity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ba238-159">있다고 가정 `myPath` 기존 <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ba238-159">It is assumed that `myPath` is an existing <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
PathGradientBrush pgBrush = new PathGradientBrush(myPath);  
 pgBrush.ResetTransform();  
```
